00:01:27.330 --> 00:01:29.729
&gt;&gt; Greek life has been at UT for a hundred
and twenty nine years.\

00:01:29.729 --> 00:01:34.049
&gt;&gt; There are over sixty five different chapters\
&gt;&gt; With over five thousand total members.\

00:01:34.049 --> 00:01:37.390
&gt;&gt; That's thirteen percent of the undergraduate
population.\

00:01:37.390 --> 00:01:42.780
&gt;&gt; So at least one out every ten students
in your class are going to be Greek.\

00:01:42.780 --> 00:01:46.130
&gt;&gt; Coming to college sometimes you feel a
little lost, and school's so big. And maybe

00:01:46.130 --> 00:01:49.710
you came here without all your high school
friends. And you're here alone and you wonder

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:53.880
like what am I going to do now? Who am I going
to hang out with? Or, um, what am I going

00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:57.840
to do on my weekends? And in being a part
of a Greek organization, not only do you develop

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:01.119
friendships, but also like close friendships
that you can take away after you graduate.\

00:02:01.119 --> 00:02:04.170
&gt;&gt; You know, walking around campus it's so
big, but then you see someone with Greek letters

00:02:04.170 --> 00:02:08.009
on and it's just like it brings that immediate
connection, and I think that's what's so awesome

00:02:08.009 --> 00:02:11.260
about it. It's like, "Oh, you know, I don't
know them, but they're Greek," so if I were

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:16.380
to go up to them and like just introduce myself,
it's like we already have that one thing in

00:02:16.380 --> 00:02:18.700
common.\
&gt;&gt; Being in a sorority helps you become a

00:02:18.700 --> 00:02:23.120
leader. It helps you become, um, a solid person
in the community, and people recognize you

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:26.099
for that.\
&gt;&gt; The Greek Community at UT really offers

00:02:26.099 --> 00:02:31.980
you, um, a unique look into the, uh, diverse
student body that UT attracts, and the neat

00:02:31.980 --> 00:02:34.739
things they want to do while they're here
at this university.\

00:02:34.739 --> 00:02:35.739
\
\

00:02:35.739 --> 00:02:38.919
&gt;&gt; A big part of being Greek,\
&gt;&gt; Is being the best Longhorn you can be.\

00:02:38.919 --> 00:02:43.310
&gt;&gt; Whether that's giving back to the community,\
&gt;&gt; Or taking care of business in the classroom.\

00:02:43.310 --> 00:02:46.989
&gt;&gt; Going Greek will ensure that scholarship,
service and philanthropy are going to be part

00:02:46.989 --> 00:02:51.379
of your college experience. \
\

00:02:51.379 --> 00:02:52.480
\
[music]\

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:53.480
\
